body:
@davidzchen 

> Are you modifying any files under third_party/gpus between running ./configure and bazel build?

Yes, that makes sense. I'm modifying `bazel-tensorflow/external/protobuf/BUILD` to fix [this issue here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/3097#issuecomment-244814825) and `third_party/gpus/crosstool/clang/bin/crosstool_wrapper_driver_is_not_gcc.tpl` to fix [this issue here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/190#issuecomment-244636243). I got it to compile after re-running `./configure` and `bazel build`.
